@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yhszse(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.35) * wp.exp(v1))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs((v2 + 0.09 + tmp + 0.52)))
    v1 = 0.46
    v2 = 0.58
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.79 + tmp + 0.10)) * (wp.cos(v1 + 0.39) * (tmp + 0.00 * v1 + 0.61)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.06)) + ((tmp + 0.09 + v1 + 0.38) * 0.24))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
